title: Default values are not shown in Show Report Parameters' dialog
description: The default values for report parameters are not being displayed in the 'Show Report Parameters' dialog.
OB: When opening the 'Show Report Parameters' dialog, the default values for each parameter are not shown.
EB: In the 'Show Report Parameters' dialog, the default values for each parameter should be displayed.
SR:
To reproduce: 
1. Open the 'Show Report Parameters' dialog for any report.
2. Check if the default values for each parameter are visible.
